      <title>波兰央行行长推迟降息计划 以提振兹罗提</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/polish-central-bank-delays-rate-cut-outlook-due-to-energy-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰央行行长亚当格拉宾斯基 (Adam Glapinski) 意外将降息预期推迟至 2026 年，理由是担心政府最终取消能源价格上限后通胀将再次飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/polish-central-bank-delays-rate-cut-outlook-due-to-energy-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:05:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
