    <item>
      <title>花旗银行如何在澳大利亚大规模大宗交易中损失 1700 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团本周以低于竞争对手的价格赢得了澳大利亚七年来最大的大宗交易，但交易最终却以失败告终，导致这家美国银行的账面上有大量未售出的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 03:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 计划推迟并减缓产量恢复速度，油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+宣布计划将增加供应量推迟三个月，但仍将从4月份开始向预计供应过剩的市场增加石油供应，油价在波动的交易中基本保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市陷入困境，就业市场预示美联储降息或暂停：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市难以在历史高点附近获得支撑，交易员们正在为至关重要的就业报告做准备，该报告将有助于确定美联储 12 月份是降息还是维持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 22:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
